{"tid":660933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死者子：點可以調轉講？","createTime":"2018-05-11T06:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T14:13:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0826f5720291bc9358f26c31653f683cd973ec","tid":660933,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:12:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387257&d=mdgRpUJljFQUQVQESb%2F3fQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d7cfa865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F20387257&h=1636673c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180511/20387257</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月11日 <br />\n<br />\n死者子：點可以調轉講？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180511/large/0509sum0228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F0509sum0228.jpg&h=54a0af14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王冰蕓指作為病人家屬，不能接受醫生面見卧床的病人多次都無發現任何護理問題。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】對於醫學界於醫委會判決後群起反對，死者王肯構的兒子王冰蕓昨接受電話訪問時表示，雖然理解醫生會同情同業，但認為當年爸爸的死，涉事的主診醫生黃卓義已被醫委會裁定有不可辯解的基本責任，「巡咗咁多次房都發現唔到爸爸個造口俾紗布封到實一實，（醫生）責無旁貸，（其他醫生）點可以調轉講法呢﹖」<br />\n<br />\n王冰蕓指，理解醫生的工作量大，需要兼顧很多臨床工作，但作為病人家屬，不能接受醫生面見卧床的病人多次都無發現任何護理問題，「而且簽埋排板、醫療紀錄&hellip;&hellip;假如他日佢嚟巡你間（病）房，你會唔會覺得安全呢？」<br />\n<br />\n他稱，個人對於醫生批評醫委會的判決沒有太多感受，「但我始終相信醫委會嘅判決係公平、公道」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，不希望事件繼續發酵，否則會進一步影響醫患關係，「其實病人同醫生係唇齒相依」，期望爭論可以盡快平息。<br />\n<br />\n他亦說，當務之急應是重修醫患關係，「呢個責任，政府、醫管局都有&hellip;&hellip;我接受咁多次訪問，並唔係要挑起事端，我都想到最後，醫管局可以增加醫生人手、醫生有多啲時間睇症，咁樣醫生、病人都係雙贏」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n不滿主診須為護士失誤孭鑊　紗布封喉案2,340醫生聯署轟醫委會<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n醫生不滿凡事被祭旗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生不滿凡事被祭旗<br />\n<br />\n斥麥列菲菲雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n不滿主診須為護士失誤孭鑊紗布封喉案　2,340醫生聯署轟醫委會"},{"pid":"5f0dfbe9c01dc23b2f7311bab6c6287977b96eb8","tid":660933,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ca41b5cb4e94c4e74b569cb447e12be98afef","tid":660933,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"護士柒做就入醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依單擺到明只係護士派膠咋喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e79ab0ac909829279c2c8cfefad97ddcd7b0de6","tid":660933,"uid":16846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a4ca41b5cb4e94c4e74b569cb447e12be98afef","tid":660933,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"護士柒做就入醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依單擺到明只係護士派膠咋喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔腦容量細到唔可以想像到係兩邊都柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f6f57661a93b9420e32393076d967662251a1f","tid":660933,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a4ca41b5cb4e94c4e74b569cb447e12be98afef","tid":660933,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"護士柒做就入醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依單擺到明只係護士派膠咋喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"咁不如唔使巡房 噤係比個鐘仔你噤算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁醫生都唔使特登拎個醫療記錄睇完再問你點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7206b291fd655e4db5614946e7b3ca288f51b001